---
import Brand from '../layouts/Brand.astro';
---
<Brand title="Hosted · usejarvis" description="Get Jarvis managed — zero servers. We run the always-on brain; the pebble, your apps, and your screen stay on your machine. Request the apps you need and buy templates from the marketplace." active="hosted">
  <header class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-in">
      <p class="label-mono reveal reveal-up">Hosted</p>
      <h1 class="display-h1 reveal reveal-up">Jarvis, managed. <em>Zero servers.</em></h1>
      <p class="lead reveal reveal-up">Path 2 is for everyone who doesn't want to self-host. We run the always-on brain on our servers — the pebble, your apps, and your screen stay on your machine. Log in and it's live.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:11px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:26px" class="reveal reveal-up">
        <a class="btn-solid" href="https://opencove.host/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Get hosted · €9.99/mo</a>
        <a class="btn-border" href="/templates">Browse templates</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section"><div class="section-inner">
    <div class="feat-grid reveal reveal-up">
      <div class="feat"><span class="fk">Managed</span><span class="ft">No servers to run</span><span class="fp">We host the always-on brain via OpenCove. You log in; it's live. <b>€9.99 / month.</b></span></div>
      <div class="feat"><span class="fk">Local</span><span class="ft">Your screen stays yours</span><span class="fp">The pebble and the apps it drives run on your machine. The brain coordinates; your data stays on your hardware.</span></div>
      <div class="feat"><span class="fk">Marketplace</span><span class="ft">Request &amp; buy templates</span><span class="fp">Need an app covered? Request it, or buy a ready-made template. <b>Builders supply the coverage; you just use it.</b></span></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section section-alt"><div class="section-inner">
    <p class="label-mono reveal reveal-up">How it fits together</p>
    <h2 class="display-h2 reveal reveal-up" style="margin:12px 0 16px">One brain, your machines.</h2>
    <ul class="prose-list reveal reveal-up">
      <li><b>Assisted setup.</b> No daemon to configure — onboarding is guided, and you're working with the native path in minutes.</li>
      <li><b>Governed by default.</b> Sensitive actions wait for your approval, every tool execution is logged, and you can pause or kill it from any surface.</li>
      <li><b>Grow into it.</b> Start hosted; if you ever want to self-host and build templates, the <a href="/builders">builder path</a> is open.</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="cta-band reveal reveal-up" style="margin-top:30px">
      <div class="ctitle">Get Jarvis running today.</div>
      <div class="csub">Managed hosting via OpenCove — €9.99 / month, cancel anytime. Your apps and screen never leave your machine.</div>
      <div class="cact"><a class="btn-solid" href="https://opencove.host/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Get hosted</a><a class="btn-border" href="/trust">How we handle your data</a></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>
</Brand>
